pus. /clear dispatches + confirms + ctx.newSession resets cleanly. /compact dispatches BUT pi 0.68 ships a built-in /compact at dist/core/slash-commands.js:19 that collides with emmy's registration; pi yellow-warns "Extension command '/compact' conflicts with built-in interactive command. Skipping in autocomplete." and dispatches to its built-in instead (which calls session.compact() — same method emmy's auto-path uses). DOCUMENTED DEVIATION: emmy's profile-defined prompts/compact.md is NOT threaded through manual /compact (only through auto-path); follow-up in 03.1-03 removes emmy's registration (1-line change). **Four-way regression at e87937b:** bun test 431 pass / 1 skip / 0 fail (+19 new: 6 live-wiring + 13 slash-commands vs Plan 03-08 close 412/1); bun run typecheck 5/5 @emmy/* packages exit 0; uv run pytest tests/unit -q 144 pass / 1 skip (unchanged); uv run emmy profile validate v1+v2+v3+v3.1 all four exit 0. **v3 hash unchanged** `sha256:2beb99c773a0e425a3e485459964740640c5f3addbea186738402cf66d4d3718` (git diff profiles/qwen3.6-35b-a3b/v3/ empty). **v3.1 hash:** `sha256:fcdecb2355688167afda98f1310d5e06e2b2c039927d5dda52271fb6ad3fee5f`. **Phase 3 deliverables regression-free:** wire-through / footer / OFFLINE OK badge / feedback JSONL / HF-export / dual-sink telemetry / interactive TUI all continue to work (boot banner still green [emmy] OFFLINE OK, SP_OK canary fires). **Daily-driver unblock:** agent no longer hits the 114,688-token hard wall during normal research sessions (auto-compaction fires on the live path at D-11 soft threshold 86016); /clear exists as manual escape valve if a pathological session still wedges; RAM pressure gone (no more swap thrashing on idle emmy-serve). **Next:** Plan 03.1-02 (SearxNG self-hosted compose + web_search tool + web_fetch returned-URL bypass + 3-state badge + air-gap CI split).
